OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773936669
OL,3,CSwindon makes longlist for UK City of
OL,4,CCulture 2029
OL,6,FSwindon has made the long list for the
OL,7,FUK City of Culture 2029 title, marking
OL,8,Fa major milestone in the town's bid to
OL,9,Fshowcase its creativity and heritage.
OL,11,FIt will now receive #60,000 from the
OL,12,Fgovernment to fully develop its bid
OL,13,Fwhich needs to be finished by the
OL,14,Fsummer.
OL,16,FA shortlist will then be announced
OL,17,Flater in the year before the final
OL,18,Fwinner is confirmed in winter 2026.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
