OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773936669
OL,3,CSwindon makes longlist for UK City of
OL,4,CCulture 2029
OL,6,FThe winning city will then receive #10
OL,7,Fmillion to deliver a year's worth of
OL,8,Fcultural activities celebrating
OL,9,Fpeople, stories, and heritage.
OL,11,FThe three next most impressive bids
OL,12,Fwill receive #125,000 each to continue
OL,13,Fwith some of their planned projects.
OL,15,FThe borough council's cabinet member
OL,16,Ffor placemaking, Councillor Marina
OL,17,FStrinkovsksy, described being
OL,18,Flonglisted as an "extraordinary
OL,19,Fmoment" for the town.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773936669
OL,3,CSwindon makes longlist for UK City of
OL,4,CCulture 2029
OL,6,F"It recognises the imagination, talent
OL,7,Fand determination that have always
OL,8,Fdefined our town.
OL,10,F"This achievement belongs to every
OL,11,Fartist, volunteer, young producer,
OL,12,Fcommunity group and cultural
OL,13,Forganisation that has poured their
OL,14,Fenergy into telling Swindon's story,"
OL,15,Fshe added.
OL,17,F"We're a place built by thinkers,
OL,18,Fmakers and innovators and today's news
OL,19,Fshows that the rest of the country is
OL,20,Fbeginning to see what we've known all
OL,21,Falong.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773936669
OL,3,CSwindon makes longlist for UK City of
OL,4,CCulture 2029
OL,6,F"Longlisting gives us a powerful
OL,7,Fplatform to showcase our heritage, our
OL,8,Fambition and our belief in Swindon as
OL,9,Fa cultural powerhouse.
OL,11,F"I couldn't be prouder of what we've
OL,12,Fachieved together and I'm excited to
OL,13,Fhear if we get shortlisted."
OL,15,FSwindon will be vying against
OL,16,FSheffield, Inverness, Wrexham,
OL,17,FBlackpool, Ipswich, Middlesbrough,
OL,18,FMilton Keynes, and Portsmouth.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
