OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773936669
OL,3,CSwindon makes longlist for UK City of
OL,4,CCulture 2029
OL,6,FLeader of the Council, Councillor Jim
OL,7,FRobbins, said: "Reaching the final
OL,8,Fnine in the competition is a fantastic
OL,9,Fachievement for Swindon and a
OL,10,Ftestament to the passion and
OL,11,Fcreativity of communities in the
OL,12,Fborough.
OL,14,F"We know Swindon has an incredible
OL,15,Fstory to tell, from our rich heritage
OL,16,Fto our vibrant and growing cultural
OL,17,Fscene. Being longlisted gives us the
OL,18,Fopportunity to share that story on a
OL,19,Fnational stage and create new
OL,20,Fopportunities for residents and
OL,21,Fbusinesses alike.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
